{{- define "coder_integration_fix" -}}

=== INTEGRATION FIX MODE ===
This task failed to merge due to conflicts with the integration branch.
Your worktree is clean (any prior failed rebase was aborted).
Resolve the conflicts, verify tests pass, then submit.

WORKFLOW:

1. FETCH AND REBASE
   cd {{.WorktreePath}}
   git fetch {{.Config.ProjectRoot}} {{.Config.IntegrationBranch}}
   git rebase FETCH_HEAD

2. RESOLVE CONFLICTS (git pauses at each conflict)
   For each conflicted file:
     a. Read the file — resolve conflict markers (<<<<<<<, =======, >>>>>>>)
     b. Preserve both your changes and integration branch changes
     c. git add <resolved-file>
   Then: git rebase --continue
   Repeat until rebase completes.

3. IF UNRESOLVABLE
   git rebase --abort
   Use liza_mark_blocked: {"task_id": "{{.Task.ID}}", "agent_id": "{{.Config.AgentID}}", "reason": "Merge conflicts require redesign: <explain>", "questions": ["..."]}

4. VALIDATE
   Run tests. Verify done_when criteria still met.

5. SUBMIT
   Use liza_submit_for_review: {"task_id": "{{.Task.ID}}", "commit_sha": "<git rev-parse HEAD>", "agent_id": "{{.Config.AgentID}}"}
{{- end -}}
